The advanced pawn e5 gets a sufficient protection.} b5 $1 13. c3 Nf8 14. d4 b4
$1 {The attack on the queenside starts.} 15. Be3 $5 bxc3 16. bxc3 Qa5 $1 17.
Bf1 $6 c4 $6 ({Pirc rejected} 17... Qxc3 18. Rac1 Qa3 19. dxc5 {but} Nd7 $1 {
