Ng6 27. h5 Qb2 28. hxg6 Qxd2 29. gxf7+ Kxf7 30. Nxd2 {brings less advantage.})
26. Qg5 Ng6 27. Re1 h6 28. Qg4 Bf8 $1 29. h5 Ne7 $1 {
Black is going to gain material.} 30. Qf4 (30. Bxe7 Bxe7 31. Qf4 Qxa2 {
costs a pawn.}) 30... gxf6 31. exf6 Nec6 32. g4 Qc2 33. Qg3 Nb5 34. g5 Bd6 35.
Qg2 Kh8 $1 36. Ng3 Rg8 37. g6 fxg6 38. f7 Rg7 39. Nh4 gxh5 40. Qf3 Bf8 41. Kh1
Qxc3 42. Qf4 Rg4 43. Nxh5 $5 Qxd4 ({Not} 43... Rxf4 $4 44. Ng6+ Kh7 45. Nxf8+
